{"tid":1142480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佔中案裁決】邵家臻押往赤柱監獄 高呼：香港撐住！","createTime":"2019-05-07T05:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T05:58:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5be7685cff8b8c0addd5926725eed7cb0433e461","tid":1142480,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190507/59572272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59572272&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=d6d109b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59572272&h=49da5c19\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190507/59572272</a><br />\n<br />\n【佔中案裁決】邵家臻押往赤柱監獄 高呼：香港撐住！<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後更新: 0507 12:03 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0507 11:23<br />\n<br />\n「佔中案」中被判入獄8個月的立法會社福界議員邵家臻，進行俗稱「通波仔」的冠狀動脈介入治療手術後留醫數天，今日被送往赤柱監獄，與黃浩銘同一監獄服刑。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陳淑莊敲定日子動腦手術 市民贈冷帽御守集氣<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻議員辦事處指：「（邵家臻）家人剛收到福利官通知，邵家臻會去赤柱，已出車。」<br />\n上午11時40分左右，兩名懲教員押解邵家臻離開醫院。邵身穿囚衣，雙手被扣上手鐐，腰纏鎖鏈，拿住一袋個人物品。手術後的邵家臻精神不錯，登上囚車前振臂高呼：「撐住、撐住，香港撐住、撐住香港！」<br />\n<br />\n「佔中案」上月24日判刑，發起佔中的三子被判入獄16個月，當中朱耀明緩刑兩年。邵家臻及黃浩銘須即時入獄8個月、張秀賢被判接受200小時社會服務令、鍾耀華及李永達被判入獄8個月，緩刑兩年。陳淑莊因健康問題獲准押後判刑。<br />\n<br />\n現時戴耀廷在大嶼山石壁監獄服刑，陳健民及黃浩銘則分別在西貢壁屋及赤柱監獄服刑。邵家臻於判刑後還押荔枝角收押所，翌日因血壓偏高送往伊利沙伯醫院羈留病房留醫。他較早前向懲教署申請出席立法會會議，但已被拒絕其申請。<br />\n<br />\n【六四30】守住歷史 拒絕遺忘<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.adai.ly/zdzKtt2RiW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.adai.ly%2FzdzKtt2RiW&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=0957a4ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.adai.ly/zdzKtt2RiW</a><br />\n5月7日7pm <br />\n玩《MINI GAME大挑戰》<br />\nCIELO絲悅送出400份慕絲染髮劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WigzsG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WigzsG&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=8019d754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WigzsG</a><br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 立即WhatsApp《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 或致電：63836568  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557201788_e0ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557201788_e0ec.jpg&h=a714c056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邵家臻由醫院被押解到赤柱監獄服刑。劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557202037_303c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557202037_303c.jpg&h=ecd6bafd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557201412_cee7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557201412_cee7.jpg&h=4484493a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邵家臻拿住個人物品離開醫院。劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557201412_2952.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557201412_2952.jpg&h=642e620a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邵家臻由懲教員押走。劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557203887_3faf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557203887_3faf.jpg&h=62414d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n載住邵家臻的囚車，駛入赤柱監獄。胡恩宏攝<br />\n<br />\n 上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【中美貿易戰】習拒大讓步「所有後果我一人負責」 被侵侵出招陷兩難<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【血統超早熟】阿爸係兩歲短途王 「伯樂」仔三歲黃金期<br />\n<br />\n陳淑莊敲定日子動腦手術 市民贈冷帽御守集氣"}]}